title: How to Make Eggless Corn Bread

steps.headline: Beat all of the ingredients together thoroughly.
Bake in a moderate oven for 20 minutes.
Remove from oven and allow to cool on a wire cake rack.

text: Beat all of the ingredients together thoroughly.  Pour mixture into muffin pans.  Bake in a moderate oven for 20 minutes.  Remove from oven and allow to cool on a wire cake rack.  Finished.
